{"type":"message","id":"cf5c4da0","parentId":"2a0db947","timestamp":"2026-03-01T00:35:20.093Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_70ddf82f0e0e402b8b264783","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-02-28 - 日志层\n\n## 📝 今日活动\n\n### 凌晨 (00:00 UTC)\n- **每日复盘执行**: 执行了完整的每日复盘流程，包括备份、内省、反思和更新\n- **Git备份尝试**: 成功执行了git add和commit，但push失败（远程仓库配置问题）\n- **记忆系统回顾**: 完整回顾了分层记忆结构和近期项目状态\n- **配置状态确认**: 确认了当前的AGENTS.md、MEMORY.md等核心配置文件状态\n\n### 技术要点\n- 识别出git远程仓库配置需要修复\n- 确认了AI IoT设备市场分析项目的持续进行\n- 验证了记忆分层系统的有效性\n\n### 待办事项\n- 修复git远程仓库配置，确保备份能正常push\n- 继续推进AI IoT设备市场分析（每日9:00 UTC）\n- 跟进Project Emerald的PostgreSQL安装状态"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772325320092}}
{"type":"message","id":"08aefaf7","parentId":"cf5c4da0","timestamp":"2026-03-01T00:35:22.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c7ec7c369d55428c9f0e0f58","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/projects.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":14518,"output":28,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14546,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772325320093}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b8690c2","parentId":"08aefaf7","timestamp":"2026-03-01T00:35:22.212Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c7ec7c369d55428c9f0e0f58","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Projects Status\n\n## AI IoT Devices Market Analysis\nStatus: Active\nDescription: Daily analysis of AI-powered ESP32 devices for 2C market\nSchedule: Daily at 9:00 UTC\nFocus: Simple, manufacturable products with overseas market potential\nPriority: High\n\n## Current Product Ideas\n1. Smart Plant Care Device - Soil + light monitoring with AI watering suggestions\n2. Personal Health Monitor Patch - Temperature/heart rate with anomaly alerts  \n3. Home Security Sound Sentinel - Audio anomaly detection (glass break, baby cry)\n4. Pet Behavior Monitor - Activity pattern analysis with abnormal behavior alerts\n5. Air Quality Smart Alert - PM2.5/CO2/VOC monitoring with health recommendations"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772325322210}}
{"type":"message","id":"d492b8ea","parentId":"1b8690c2","timestamp":"2026-03-01T00:35:24.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c1735a9dc9674e6bb3c9f2dc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/lessons.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":14707,"output":29,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14736,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772325322212}}
{"type":"message","id":"d127595b","parentId":"d492b8ea","timestamp":"2026-03-01T00:35:24.972Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c1735a9dc9674e6bb3c9f2dc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Lessons Learned - 教训层\n\n踩过的坑，按严重程度分级。\n\n## 🔴 严重 (Critical)\n- **OpenClaw 配置位置**: memorySearch 配置必须放在 `agents.defaults` 下，不能在根级别\n- **JSON 格式要求**: 配置文件必须是严格的 JSON 格式，不能使用 JavaScript 语法\n\n## 🟠 中等 (Medium)\n- **PostgreSQL 端口**: Ubuntu 24.04 默认可能未安装 PostgreSQL，需要手动安装和配置端口 5433\n- **内存查看**: Linux 内存显示中 `available` 比 `free` 更重要，因为系统会用空闲内存做缓存\n\n## 🟢 轻微 (Low)\n- **Git 分支管理**: 开发新功能时应该创建专门的分支（如 `openclaw`）而不是直接在主分支工作\n- **API 密钥安全**: 敏感信息如 API keys 不应该硬编码在共享配置中\n\n## 💡 最佳实践\n- **记忆分层**: 使用索引层 + 项目层 + 基础设施层 + 教训层 + 日志层的结构\n- **主动保存**: 重要的对话内容需要明确指令才会持久化到记忆文件\n- **定期清理**: 定期回顾和整理 MEMORY.md，保持核心信息的准确性\n- **Git 配置**: 确保远程仓库正确配置，避免备份失败"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772325324970}}
